該片的[[主體攝影|主體攝影]]於2013年7月在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]開始<ref name=release>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/jon-favreaus-chef-set-for-u-s-distribution-with-open-road-1200496258/|title=Jon Favreau’s ‘Chef’ Set For U.S. Distribution with Open Road|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2014-06-12|first=Dave|last=McNary|accessdate=2014-07-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304121404/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/jon-favreaus-chef-set-for-u-s-distribution-with-open-road-1200496258/|archivedate=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後，拍攝作業移至[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]、[[奧斯汀|奧斯汀]]與[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]進行。法夫洛之所以選擇在這些城市取景，是因為它們全都「充滿了豐富的美食與音樂文化」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cntraveler.com/daily-traveler/2014/05/on-location-with-chef-director-jon-favreau|title=On Location with 'Chef' Director Jon Favreau in Miami, Austin, and New Orleans|first=Jennifer M.|last=Wood|work={{link-en|康德納斯旅行者|Condé Nast Traveler|Condé Nast Traveler}}|date=2014-05-08|accessdate=2014-07-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161206172230/http://www.cntraveler.com/stories/2014-05-08/on-location-with-chef-director-jon-favreau|archivedate=2016-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中較著名的取景地點，包含邁阿密的{{link-en|凡爾賽餐廳|Versailles restaurant}}、{{link-en|楓丹白露邁阿密海灘|Fontainebleau Miami Beach|楓丹白露酒店}}與[[小哈瓦那|小哈瓦那]]的古巴餐廳「{{lang|en|Hoy Como Ayer}}」<ref name=Eater>{{cite news|title=Jon Favreau's Chef Film Is Shooting in Miami|url=http://eater.com/archives/2013/08/13/favreaumobile.php|accessdate=2014-07-14|newspaper=Eater|date=2013-08-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303190803/http://www.eater.com/2013/8/13/6387407/jon-favreaus-chef-film-is-shooting-in-miami|archivedate=2017-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=MiamiNewTimes>{{cite news|title=Jon Favreau, Sofia Vergara Filming Chef in Miami This Week|url=http://blogs.miaminewtimes.com/cultist/2013/08/jon_favreau_sofia_vergara_film.php|accessdate=2014-07-14|newspaper={{link-en|邁阿密時報|Miami New Times|Miami New Times}}|date=2013-08-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222144103/http://www.miaminewtimes.com/arts/jon-favreau-sofia-vergara-filming-chef-in-miami-this-week-6492277|archivedate=2015-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在紐奧良拍攝時，部分場景在[[法国区|法国区]]的[[世界咖啡馆|世界咖啡馆]]攝影<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2014/05/chef_director_jon_favreaus_new.html|work={{link-en|皮卡尤恩時報|The Times-Picayune|The Times-Picayune}}|title=Jon Favreau's New Orleans: 'Chef' director embraces sounds, flavors of the Crescent City in his film|first=Mike|last=Scott|date=2014-05-22|accessdate=2014-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223850/http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2014/05/chef_director_jon_favreaus_new.html|archivedate=2016-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。劇組於奧斯汀的取景地點包含{{link-en|富蘭克林燒烤|Franklin Barbecue}}及{{link-en|南方國會|South Congress}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://austin.eater.com/2013/8/21/6383587/chef-filming-at-franklin-bbq-headed-to-gueros-next |title=Chef Filming at Franklin BBQ, Headed to Guero's Next |newspaper=Eater |date=2013-08-21 |accessdate=2015-02-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005021754/http://austin.eater.com/2013/8/21/6383587/chef-filming-at-franklin-bbq-headed-to-gueros-next |archivedate=2016-10-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。片中所有烹調的菜餚，都會在拍攝結束後由全體演員與工作人員共同享用<ref name=vulture/>。

