== 上映 ==

《五星主廚快餐車》於2014年3月7日以開幕片的身分在[[西南偏南|西南偏南]]（SXSW）首映，法夫洛、李昆薩默、安東尼與普雷特皆出席了首映典禮<ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/03/08/sxsw-fest-opens-with-world-premiere-of-jon-favreaus-chef/|work=[[娛樂周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|title=SXSW: Fest opens with world premiere of Jon Favreau's 'Chef'|date=2014-03-08|first=Karen|last=Valby|accessdate=2014-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305231822/http://www.ew.com/article/2014/03/08/sxsw-fest-opens-with-world-premiere-of-jon-favreaus-chef|archivedate=2016-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後，電影在4月份於[[翠貝卡電影節|翠貝卡電影節]]上進行放映<ref name=vulture/>。8月19日，開路影業宣布，該片將會在8月29日美國[[劳动节_(美国)|勞動節]]時重新在全國廣泛發行，上映劇院數會從100家增加為600至800家<ref>{{cite news|title=‘Chef’ Cooks Up Awards Plan With Labor Day Weekend Re-Release|url=http://deadline.com/2014/08/chef-movie-rerelease-august-29-jon-favreau-821752/|accessdate=2014-08-20|publisher=deadline.com|date=2014-08-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224224421/http://deadline.com/2014/08/chef-movie-rerelease-august-29-jon-favreau-821752/|archivedate=2017-02-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影的[[藍光光碟|藍光]]及[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]版本於9月30日發布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/6450/Chef.html |title=Chef (2014) |publisher=DVDsReleaseDates.com |date= |accessdate=2014-09-30 |archive-date=2019-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515034619/https://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/6450/Chef.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 反響 ==

=== 評價 ===

[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的174篇專業影評文章中，有150篇給予該片「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為86%，平均得分6.8分（滿分10分）。該網站的共識性評價寫道「《五星主廚快餐車》的迷人演員及犀利、有趣的劇本為其增添了足夠的笑料，使這部令人愉悅的喜劇成了更加夠味的饗宴——前提是你得先熟悉它」<ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chef_2014/ | title= Chef (2014) | publisher= [[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate= 2017-03-09 | archive-date= 2020-11-18 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201118150926/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chef_2014 | dead-url= no }}</ref>。而基於另一影評匯總網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的36篇評論文章中，有25篇予以好評，2篇差評，9篇褒貶不一，平均分為68（滿分100），綜合結果為「普遍良好的評價」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/chef|title=Chef reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111192208/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/chef|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》的[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]給予電影3.5顆星（滿分4星）的評價，將其描述為「一個巧妙的驚喜和非凡的禮物」及「令人發笑、動容且不時對現實世界進行尖酸諷刺的清爽娛樂」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/chef-20140508|title=Chef|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]]|first=Peter|last=Travers|date=2014-05-08|accessdate=2014-07-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231000059/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/chef-20140508|archivedate=2016-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[波士頓環球報|波士頓環球報]]》的[[泰·布爾|泰·布爾]]也打出了3.5顆星（滿分4星）的分數；認為電影「有趣且真誠」，儘管它有著不可否認的缺點，但優點「壓過了火候不足的部分」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/arts/movies/2014/05/15/cooking-from-heart-chef/HbOBia4GKHU1rgyroiPglN/story.html|title=Cooking from the heart in 'Chef'|first=Ty|last=Burr|date=2014-05-15|work=[[波士頓環球報|Boston Globe]]|accessdate=2014-07-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308035121/https://www.bostonglobe.com/arts/movies/2014/05/15/cooking-from-heart-chef/HbOBia4GKHU1rgyroiPglN/story.html|archivedate=2016-03-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的{{link-en|理察·羅珀|Richard Roeper}}對《五星主廚快餐車》的評分為3顆星（滿分4星），認為其「有趣、古靈精怪且富洞察力」，但同時也注意到些許部分缺乏劇情及角色的發展<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/27402577-421/chef-a-funny-story-then-a-long-dinner-break.html |title='Chef': A funny story, then a long dinner break |date=2014-05-15 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |work=[[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun-Times]] |first=Richard |last=Roeper |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529123900/http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/27402577-421/chef-a-funny-story-then-a-long-dinner-break.html |archivedate=2014-05-29 }}</ref>。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的蓋瑞·哥德斯坦稱讚了「優秀的配角演員」及新穎的劇本，如家庭互動方面的表現<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-chef-movie-review-20140509-story.html|title=Jon Favreau's 'Chef' has all the ingredients for a hit|first=Gary|last=Goldstein|date=2014-05-08|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate=2014-07-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108091033/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-chef-movie-review-20140509-story.html|archivedate=2017-01-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

不過有些影評人給出的評價並不大正面。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌的喬·蘭登發覺該片的劇情可被預料且節奏緩慢，並指出「旅行本身远不只有那些令人愉快、让人开怀大笑的东西」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/sxsw-film-review-chef-1201128175/|title=SXSW Film Review: ‘Chef’|date=2014-03-08|first=Joe|last=Leydon|accessdate=2014-07-16|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405131339/http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/sxsw-film-review-chef-1201128175/|archivedate=2016-04-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的麥克·歐蘇利文給予電影3.5顆星（滿分4星）的評價，察覺其「使人打從心靈深處感到心滿意足」，並盛讚片中「不可思議」的攝影技巧、「多采多姿的配角演員」及來自「帶諷刺意味的」的犀利笑點<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/chef-movie-review-jon-favreau-makes-a-satisfying-return-to-his-indie-roots/2014/05/14/08f3ec38-db7d-11e3-bda1-9b46b2066796_story.html|title='Chef' movie review: Jon Favreau makes a satisfying return to his indie roots|first=Michael|last=O'Sullivan|date=2014-05-15|work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]]|accessdate=2014-07-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517170854/https://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/chef-movie-review-jon-favreau-makes-a-satisfying-return-to-his-indie-roots/2014/05/14/08f3ec38-db7d-11e3-bda1-9b46b2066796_story.html|archivedate=2017-05-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]]》的米克·拉塞勒認為，《五星主廚快餐車》是法夫洛迄今最佳的電影作品，並稱讚法夫洛和安東尼之間「自然并令人信服」的火花，及由大咖演員飾演小角色的特點<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Chef-review-A-first-class-meal-5480913.php|title='Chef' review: A first-class meal|date=2014-05-15|accessdate=2014-07-16|first=Mick|last=LaSalle|work=[[舊金山紀事報|San Francisco Chronicle]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304235754/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Chef-review-A-first-class-meal-5480913.php|archivedate=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的史考特·鮑爾斯打出了3.5顆星（滿分4星）的分數，稱該片為「一道細緻的配菜」及「一部細火慢熬的電影」，並表示「《五星主廚快餐車》是年初最為溫馨的電影之一」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/05/08/chef-review/8314715/|date=2014-05-08|title='Chef' melds ingredients for a fine family comedy|first=Scott|last=Bowles|work=[[今日美國|USA Today]]|accessdate=2014-07-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204130644/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/05/08/chef-review/8314715/|archivedate=2016-02-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Wide Lantern》的肯·崔注意到了結構上的問題，但承認「我在看電影下半段時，我的淚水不曾停下來過。我為法夫洛的角色正在做他所想做之事而喜極而泣」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://widelantern.com/2014/10/chef-cooks-up-faves/ |title=Chef Cooks Up Faves |publisher=Wide Lantern |date=2014-12-04 |accessdate=2015-03-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331141914/http://widelantern.com/2014/10/chef-cooks-up-faves/ |archivedate=2016-03-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[偏鋒雜誌|偏鋒雜誌]]》的影評人克里斯·卡賓對《五星主廚快餐車》的評分僅有1.5顆星（滿分4星），批評該片缺乏真實感和可信度<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/film/review/chef|first=Chris|last=Cabin|title=Chef|work=[[偏鋒雜誌|Slant Magazine]]|date=2014-04-23|accessdate=2014-07-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211193902/http://www.slantmagazine.com/film/review/chef|archivedate=2015-12-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{link-en|鄉村之音|The Village Voice}}》的艾米·尼科爾森認為，該片的劇情不合情理<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2014-05-07/film/chef-movie-review/|title=With Chef, Jon Favreau Whips Up Indie Comfort Food|date=2014-05-07|first=Amy|last=Nicholson|work={{link-en|鄉村之音|The Village Voice|The Village Voice}}|accessdate=2014-07-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530103609/http://www.villagevoice.com/film/with-chef-jon-favreau-whips-up-indie-comfort-food-6441795|archivedate=2016-05-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]的艾瑞克·科恩對《五星主廚快餐車》表達了看法，「法夫洛沒有貫徹任何主題或想法」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/sxsw-review-is-jon-favreaus-chef-a-return-to-indie-form-only-in-the-context-of-his-own-career|title=SXSW Review: Is Jon Favreau's 'Chef' a Return to Indie Form? Only In the Context of His Own Career|first=Eric|last=Kohn|date=2014-03-08|accessdate=2014-07-22|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312151708/http://www.indiewire.com/2014/03/sxsw-review-is-jon-favreaus-chef-a-return-to-indie-form-only-in-the-context-of-his-own-career-29230/|archivedate=2017-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===

電影於2014年5月9日開始在美國發行，最初僅在6家劇院[[有限上映|有限上映]]。劇院數量在6月的上旬及中旬達到巔峰，最多時共有1,298家劇院放映該片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekly&id=chef.htm|title=Chef: Weekly|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514215431/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekly&id=chef.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至8月17日，美國票房總計為2,930萬美元<ref name=bom />。

於美國以外，《五星主廚快餐車》在-{zh-cn:澳大利亚;zh-tw:澳洲;zh-hk:澳洲}-（280萬美元）、英國（260萬美元）與西班牙（收入逾100萬美元）的票房表現最佳。總體而言，電影於美國以外地區所進帳的票房將近1,500萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=chef.htm|title=Chef: Foreign|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515173609/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=chef.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

